reviewText: Second time reordering this and still will not work! Returned it once more and will not buy again
Doesn't work in US DVD player. Very disappointed!!!!
Had to return couldn't use this it is a European DVD
Beware this doesn't play in regular DVD players. You can only use it on a computer

Very Pleased. Jungle Junction is on Disney Junior TV and the Grand Kids like it a lot.  It is only available on Non-USA format DVD's so we bought an ALL Region DVD player to be able to play this and other Disney DVD's not available for play in the US.  Is a Great show and only wish that there were more DVD's available in this series.  Recommend it highly to Parents / Grand Parents with young Children.
Seller shipped and item delivered quickly.

My 2 year old loves this show. We bought this to take along on a trip to Vegas. I think the description could be a little clearer though. I was under the impression that I was getting the season and not a few episodes. (I still would've bought it just wouldn't have been as disappointed. ) other than that it's great but 2 stars go to misinformation
My 3 year old son loves this cartoon.  We watch this video on the computer.  Wish there were more videos available to purchase.
